WEBVTT

00:02.653 --> 00:03.337
Hello.

00:04.378 --> 00:06.565
Hello. Who is calling please?

00:07.584 --> 00:10.504
This is Erica. Can I talk to Linda?

00:11.555 --> 00:12.559
Hold on, please.

00:13.625 --> 00:15.025
This is she speaking.

00:16.063 --> 00:19.891
Hi, This is Erica. What are you doing, Linda?

00:20.969 --> 00:23.007
I was just about to clean my room.

00:24.051 --> 00:26.490
Why don't you go to see a movie with me?

00:27.523 --> 00:29.862
I do want to see a movie today!

00:30.921 --> 00:33.727
That sounds great. What time shall we meet?

00:34.791 --> 00:37.384
Let's meet at the bus stop at 3:00.

00:38.439 --> 00:40.276
OK. See you then.

